<svg class="tankan tankan-gantt" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1047.5 338" width="1047.5" height="338" role="img" aria-label="Adding GANTT diagram functionality to mermaid" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14">
<style>
.tankan text { fill: #1f2328; }
